‘Michael’ Movie Review: A ‘whitewashed’ and 'clichéd' depiction of Michael Jackson’s life
@JaafarJackson
@AntoineFuqua

Review by  @lachmi0809

@DiscussingFilm I saw the movie today, and I will rate it a 8/10.
I think they dwelt too much on Joe Jackson being an abusive father, almost every scene kept portraying him as a mean man.
Aside this, every other thing about the film was satisfactory
